      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VICTA WALLY (3) recorded his best time this course and distance latest, finishing a 0.8 lengths second behind Compton Gypsy in 30.43. Should be in this for a long way. DAKOTA AVA (4) was below best last time at Murray Bridge (22.39) in a Grade 3/4/5, finishing a 2.25 lengths fourth. Has already won five times from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. JAN HEWETT (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last five runs. Last time finished 2nd over 595m at this track beaten 2.25 lengths (34.38) behind Duran Pantera in a Grade 6/MDN on April 30. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature again. WEBLEC PRINCE (6) is always a threat when he races at this journey.",
